graph TD
    A["Incoming Fact<br/>(Subject: ${CHILD1}<br/>Relationship: age<br/>Value: 12)"] -->|Check First| B{Is This a<br/>Retraction?}

    B -->|Yes| C["Retraction Path<br/>(Remove/archive fact)"]
    C --> D["Remove or Archive<br/>Old fact from database<br/>Preserve history"]
    D --> E["Done<br/>(Skip rest)"]

    B -->|No| F{Enough<br/>Information?}
    F -->|No| G["Stop<br/>(Message too short)"]
    F -->|Yes| H["Continue"]

    H --> I{User Correction?<br/>Does user explicitly<br/>say different?}

    I -->|Yes| J["High Priority<br/>(User's input<br/>overrides everything)<br/>Trust level: 100%"]

    I -->|No| K["Normal Path"]

    J --> L["Validation Check"]
    K --> L

    L --> M["Step 1: Learn Relationship<br/>Does the system<br/>already know this<br/>relationship type?"]

    M -->|No| N["New Pattern Detected<br/>System records:<br/>- What kind of relationship<br/>- Direction (one-way/both)<br/>- Allowed types<br/>Example: age connects<br/>to numbers only"]

    M -->|Yes| O["Use Existing Rules<br/>Already know how<br/>this relationship works"]

    N --> P["Step 2: Learn Entity Type<br/>What type of thing<br/>is this entity?"]
    O --> P

    P -->|Type Unknown| Q["Classify Entity<br/>Example: ${CHILD1} is a Person<br/>System records this"]

    P -->|Type Known| R["Use Existing Type"]

    Q --> S["Check for Conflicts<br/>(Does this make sense?)<br/>Example: Can't say<br/>John is a person AND<br/>John is a company"]
    R --> S

    S -->|Conflict Found| T["Keep the trusted fact<br/>Remove the conflicting one"]

    S -->|No Conflict| U["Check Consistency<br/>If a relationship is<br/>bidirectional, make sure<br/>both directions match"]

    T --> U

    U -->|Consistent| V{Where to Store?}

    V -->|Simple Value<br/>age, name, height| W["Store as Attribute<br/>(One value per entity)<br/>${CHILD1}.age = 12"]

    V -->|Classification<br/>instance_of, subclass_of| X["Store as Classification<br/>(Type hierarchy)<br/>${CHILD1} is-a Person<br/>Person is-a Organism"]

    V -->|Relationship<br/>spouse, parent_of| Y["Store as Relationship<br/>(Connections)<br/>${CHILD1} connects-to User<br/>as parent_of"]

    W --> Z{Assess Trust Level}
    X --> Z
    Y --> Z

    Z -->|User Stated<br/>High confidence| AA["Trusted (100%)<br/>Save to database<br/>immediately"]

    Z -->|LLM Inferred<br/>from known patterns| AB["Probable (80%)<br/>Hold for review<br/>Save if user<br/>confirms 3 times"]

    Z -->|New Pattern<br/>Uncertain| AC["Experimental (40%)<br/>Hold for system<br/>to evaluate<br/>Auto-delete<br/>if unused 30 days"]

    AA --> AD["Write to Database<br/>(Permanent fact)"]
    AB --> AE["Write to Staging<br/>(Waiting for confirmation)"]
    AC --> AE

    AD --> AF["Background Sync<br/>(Index in search)<br/>Process confirmations<br/>Evaluate new patterns)"]
    AE --> AF

    AF --> AG["Complete<br/>Fact ready for<br/>retrieval"]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style E fill:#c8e6c9
    style N fill:#f3e5f5
    style Q fill:#f3e5f5
    style W fill:#fff9c4
    style X fill:#fff9c4
    style Y fill:#fff9c4
    style AA fill:#c8e6c9
    style AB fill:#ffffcc
    style AC fill:#e0e0e0
    style AG fill:#c8e6c9
